At the airport

Baggage



Baggage


Baggage changes 
Baggage fees have changed for Colombia and Venezuela for trips booked on or after April 12, 2017.


Optional service fees				   
												
												
													







Our policies



Checked baggage
From charges to weight and size, here's everything about our checked baggage policy.


										See our checked baggage policies
										
											





Carry-on baggage
Make your journey easier and discover what to expect when packing your carry-on bag.


										See our carry-on policy
										
											





Restricted items
There are many common items that are restricted by the TSA.


										See our restricted items
										
											









Specialty and sports
From musical instruments to military baggage, here's everything you need to know.


										See our specialty and sports policies
										
											





Traveling with pets
We’re making your pet our priority. Here are some guidelines to help make your journey smoother.


										Find out more about traveling with pets
										
											





Traveling with children
Taking a trip with your child or infant can be child’s play. We’ll show you how.


										Learn about traveling with children or infants
										
											











First checked bag free on domestic itineraries 
Earn 30,000 bonus miles after qualifying purchases
Your first checked bag is free on domestic itineraries for you and up to four people traveling with you with select Citi® / AAdvantage®  cards. 


										Learn more about this offer
																					
											Opens another site in a new window that may not meet accessibility guidelines





										Already a cardholder? Learn more about your card’s benefits
										
											











Luggage delivery service
Bypass baggage claim
Whether you're traveling for business or pleasure on your next trip, let us bring your bags to you.


										Learn more about our luggage delivery service
										
											






Flying on one of our partners?
From seating policy to lounge information, here’s everything you need to know about flying with our partner airlines.


										Find out more about traveling with oneworld 
										
											




										Finnair baggage policies
																					
											Opens another site in a new window that may not meet accessibility guidelines






										British Airways baggage policies
																					
											Opens another site in a new window that may not meet accessibility guidelines





										Iberia baggage policies
																					
											Opens another site in a new window that may not meet accessibility guidelines











Lost an item?
We can help you 
If you’ve lost an item on a plane or in an American-operated area, at the airport or at a security checkpoint, visit our lost and found page and we’ll point you in the right direction.


										Go to lost and found
										
											






Special assistance
Let us take care of you 
We offer assistance at the airport, on the plane and upon arrival for a variety of needs including traveling with devices, disabilities, children and more.


										Learn more about special assistance
										
											




