American Airlines Inc: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback















american airlines inc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Consumer Discretionary
Industry: Passenger Transportation
Sub-Industry: Airlines
American Airlines, Inc. offers airline services. The Company provides scheduled air transportation services for passengers and cargo. American Airlines serves customers worldwide.




